	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Node: Camk2a | PMID: 15664178 | Assay: In vitro protein kinase assay | Biological system: Purified recombinant proteins (E. coli expressed His6-STG and rat brain CaMKII) | Fig: 5C | Note: \"CaMKII specifically phosphorylated the cytoplasmic tail of stargazin\""^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> , "Node: Cacng2 | PMID: 15664178 | Assay: Metabolic labeling with [32P]orthophosphate and 2D-TLC phosphopeptide mapping | Biological system: Primary cerebrocortical neuron cultures and CHO cells | Fig: 2A-D | Note: \"We performed extensive mutagenesis of the serine residues within the cytoplasmic tail... and we identified nine specific serines that contribute to the complex pattern of phosphopeptides."^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> , "Edge: Prkca -> Cacng2 | PMID: 15664178 | Assay: In vitro protein kinase assay | Biological system: Purified recombinant proteins | Fig: 5C | Note: \"Both CaMKII and PKC phosphorylated the purified C-terminal cytoplasmic domain of stargazin (STG-cyto) in vitro.\""^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> , "Edge: Camk2a -> Cacng2 | PMID: 15664178 | Assay: Pharmacological inhibition | Biological system: Primary cerebrocortical neuron cultures | Fig: 5B | Note: \"Recovery of phosphorylation after NMDA treatment was inhibited by... 20 μM KN93 (CaMKII inhibitor)\""^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> , "Node: Prkca | PMID: 15664178 | Assay: In vitro protein kinase assay | Biological system: Purified recombinant proteins (E. coli expressed His6-STG and rat brain PKC) | Fig: 5C | Note: \"the tail of stargazin was efficiently phosphorylated by PKC\""^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> , "Edge: Camk2a -> Cacng2 | PMID: 15664178 | Assay: In vitro protein kinase assay | Biological system: Purified recombinant proteins | Fig: 5C | Note: \"Both CaMKII and PKC phosphorylated the purified C-terminal cytoplasmic domain of stargazin (STG-cyto) in vitro.\""^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> , "Edge: Camk2a/Prkca -> Cacng2 | PMID: 15664178 | Assay: Whole-cell patch clamp electrophysiology | Biological system: Rat hippocampal slice cultures | Fig: 5D | Note: \"LTP with a pairing protocol yielded a robust potentiation in synaptic strength, and this was completely prevented in neurons infected with a nonphosphorylatable (S9A) version of stargazin\""^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> , "Edge: Prkca -> Cacng2 | PMID: 15664178 | Assay: Pharmacological inhibition | Biological system: Primary cerebrocortical neuron cultures | Fig: 5B | Note: \"Recovery of phosphorylation after NMDA treatment was inhibited by either 1 μM GF109203X (PKC inhibitor)\""^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> ;
